We make this request since it happens
that  
the SLB did not authorize or permitted by any means, these
users/developers  
to use the name or the emblem and its trademarks, of SLBenfica (SLB.)
Moreover, and as you can confirm, there is an association of this APP with
 
SLB, so these users/developers are taking advantage of the good name, fame
 
and prestige of the SLB, and can even  lead to confusion or error for the 

users who have the application leading them to believe that it is from
SLB.
-All of the following names are trademarks / names protected by Sport  
Lisboa e Benfica.
1.	Benfica
2.	Sport Lisboa e Benfica
3.	SL Benfica
4.	SLB
5.	SLBenfica
